Title: Fixed activation of event console log levels
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: ec
Date: 1659013414
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0p28

Changing the log levels for the event console only didn't have an effect
when it was triggered via the GUI, only when the EC was restarted.  This has
been fixed.

